{{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- Please place categories where indicated at the bottom of this page and interwikis at Wikidata (see [[Wikipedia:Wikidata]]) -->
{{High-use|394663}} 
{{Lua|Module:Taxonbar/candidate|Module:Taxonbar/exists|Module:ResolveEntityId}}
{{Lua sidebar|title=Taxonbar/candidate}}

== About ==
This template is designed to be called from {{tl|Taxobox/core}} or a related template, and tracks pages which may be candidates for a {{tl|Taxonbar}}.

If no {{tl|Taxonbar}} exists on the transcluded page, the page's Wikidata item is checked against [[Module:Taxonbar/whitelist|this whitelist]] of acceptable {{Wdpl|P31}}s/{{Wdpl|279}}s, and [[Module:Taxonbar/blacklist|this blacklist]] of ''un''acceptable properties.

If an acceptable instance/subclass is found, then the page is categorized as:
* {{clc|Category:Taxobox articles missing a taxonbar}}
If no acceptables nor ''un''acceptables are found, then it is categorized as:
* {{clc|Category:Taxobox articles possibly missing a taxonbar}}
If no acceptables & at least 1 ''un''acceptable is found, then no categorization is performed.

== Usage ==
{{tlx|Taxonbar/candidate}}

== Associated lists ==
{{columns-start}}
'''Whitelist'''
{{Taxonbar/whitelist|doc}}
{{column}}
'''Blacklist'''
{{Taxonbar/blacklist}}
{{columns-end}}

<includeonly>{{sandbox other||
<!-- Categories below this line, please; interwikis at Wikidata -->
[[Category:Templates that add a tracking category]]
}}</includeonly>

